@node tooltypes " Icon tooltypes"



@{FG SHINE}Available tooltypes:@{FG TEXT}



   @{B}DIR@{UB} - skin's catalog name



   @{B}AGA@{UB} - turn off transparency on AGA chipset



   @{B}NPB@{UB} - switches off the skin loading progress bar



   @{B}NOBORDER@{UB} - removes the frame border around the board of the game



   @{B}PP@{UB} - change the blocks' animation mode (according to skin)



   @{B}EXTRAGFX@{UB} - activates additional graphic effects (useful on better hardware configurations)



   @{B}SOUND@{UB} - sound ON.



@endnode

